{"tid":1340730,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗業主/準元朗業主入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:46.000Z","uid":236171,"like":144,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd9b438f82dd63cd24cdc2ad71cfe2a0fa9999d","tid":1340730,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"睇完今晚新聞，你地有咩感想？<br />\n<br />\n入元朗住，入元朗校網，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仔女班同學/朋友既老豆老母<br />\n就係呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以後行街俾人打劫強姦，<br />\n報咗警，差人會同你講：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">驚就唔好出街</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你嗰區既議員會同黑社會打成一遍<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係 LITERALLY 攞埋碌棍落街打成一遍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n想幫你地掃下雞竇、減少下擾民自由行<br />\n義士俾人趕走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遲下藥房越開越多、你老公日日俾北姑嬲</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每逢遊行，有人話要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">燒你屋企、拆你祠堂</span></strong><br />\n（利申，網上見到）<br />\n<br />\n以前同人講住元朗<br />\n朋友：你騎牛翻學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家同人講住元朗<br />\n朋友：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你老豆就係亂打人班鄉下佬？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>業主，你真係想喺呢個環境生存（無錯，唔係生活，係生存）落去？<br />\n<br />\n準業主，你甘心用血汗錢接火棒？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n錢係你既，自己諗喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237da21317c4663fc66b5a7900f4f27e1efacf2c","tid":1340730,"uid":30169,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"永不考慮"},{"pid":"5e5bad16bf73a1684ae65cf80d833916ae288cf7","tid":1340730,"uid":268801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:07.000Z","msg":"諗都唔好諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又危險又教壞人"},{"pid":"1a0fdcf69d720f3718ccce150685b82cab9cb175","tid":1340730,"uid":10220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件</code></pre>"},{"pid":"27ff09af1fa49a4fb667a39a66a16fd5ad9038f5","tid":1340730,"uid":47558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方, 永不考慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcccdcdef6da58d525433533e5529a9459d79474","tid":1340730,"uid":29608,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"本身想換樓入元朗，now black listed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0838430f35c53499cdbd126901cdf4fa4a3562f8","tid":1340730,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prJ0dv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FprJ0dv1.jpg&h=85959769&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6df95e2e471012fd227259d0e92afe83f927f0f2","tid":1340730,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5adf81c0d7bb81294c019e6245b6103eb95bc43e","tid":1340730,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方！"},{"pid":"02720a441372d7b2210b35faebbd6451cb5e0fac","tid":1340730,"uid":117435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"幾個月前買樓考慮過元朗<br />\n好彩因爲當時元朗太貴選擇左買第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日睇番真係執番身彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ec50eb9d9d41bc259e918e966bbb7cd9363eac","tid":1340730,"uid":83803,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"買康城好過啦<br />\n起碼唔會有班垃圾牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c1c2aeb665520e019bf0e8758e40a5e60f3d5c","tid":1340730,"uid"